Class Copycdwalite

java.lang.Object
  ORG.oclc.oai.server.crosswalk.Crosswalk
      ORG.oclc.oai.server.crosswalk.XSLTCrosswalk
          ORG.oclc.oai.server.crosswalk.Copycdwalite

public class Copycdwalite
extends XSLTCrosswalk

Convert native "item" to xsd. In this case, the native "item" is assumed to already be formatted as an OAI element, with the possible exception that multiple metadataFormats may be present in the element. The "crosswalk", merely involves pulling out the one that is requested.
